A network error: A network error caused the media download to fail part-way.
Format is not supported: The media could not be loaded, either because the server or network failed or because the format is not supported.
Media aborted or browser did not support: The media playback was aborted due to a corruption problem or because the media used features your browser did not support.
No compatible source: No compatible source was found for this media.
Media is encrypted: The media is encrypted and we do not have the keys to decrypt it.
Browser did not support: the media used features your browser did not support.
Video failed to enter PIP: Video failed to enter Picture-in-Picture mode.
Video failed to leave PIP: Video failed to leave Picture-in-Picture mode.
Try again later: The operation did not take effect. Try again later.
Successfully switched clarity: 已成功为你切换清晰度
